 };
 ```

Creating a "SORT_BY_POPULARITY" action.

```js
function sortByVotes(a, b) {
  switch(true) {
   case a.votes < b.votes: return 1;
   case a.votes > b.votes: return -1;
   default: return 0;
  }
 }
```

